title: 2020: Seth Moulton On Patriotism And Beating Trump On National Security
description: Massachusetts Congressman Seth Moulton joins Tommy Vietor to discuss the threat of nuclear war, his time in the Marine Corps and the need for a new generation of leadership in the White House.
